      "title": "Be the One (album)",
      "score": 0.09510439216942985,
      "text": "Be the One (album)\nBe the One is the second studio album by Jackie Jackson, released on September 9, 1989. The musicians included Paul Jackson, Jr., Jeff Lorber, Robert Brookins and Gerald Albright.",
